model.graph

Class AdjustableGradeRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.graph.AdjustableGradeRange

  • public class AdjustableGradeRange
extends java.lang.Object
    AdjustableGradeRange is a class which decorates the GradeRange class, it adds extra functionality to see the number of students in that grade range for a particular assignment or category.
    Author:
    erikowen
